snippet.title: The Thaumaturge | Accolades Trailer
snippet.description:
A week has passed since the release of #TheThaumaturge. We're thrilled on the reception it has received but don't take our word for it and see for yourself! 

If you haven't already, be sure to step into the dark world of 1905 Warsaw. 

Play #TheThaumaturge: http://re.11bits.com/rwq 
Follow The Thaumaturge on Twitter/X: https://twitter.com/thaumaturgegame
